            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> I'm glad that the code is minimal\r\n\r\nI love code minimality, but https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/29340 is a bit larger because it's also careful of restoring the snippet navigation keymaps when exiting the _last_ session.\r\n\r\nI also renamed `session` to `current_session`, adding a couple of changes to the diff. This is just for code clarity.\r\n\r\n> given that #29340 says \"TODO\" I'm wondering if this is actually complete.\r\n\r\nThe TODO referred to writing the PR description. I had forgotten about that PR but I'm happy to resurrect it.",
